This integrated algorithm can be used in various domains where large datasets need to be processed and analyzed. For example, in scientific research, it can be used to analyze complex molecular structures or simulate quantum systems. 
In finance, it can be applied to analyze market trends and optimize investment strategies. 
In healthcare, it can aid in analyzing patient data for personalized medicine. 
The immersive virtual reality visualization enhances the understanding and exploration of the processed data, enabling users to gain deeper insights and make informed decisions.
